quran[339]{c,v,t}:
  25,21,WE KALEL-LEDHINE LA JERXHUNE LIKA’ENA LEWLA ‘UNZILE ‘ALEJNAL-MELA’IKETU ‘EW NERA REBBENA LEKADI ESTEKBERU FI ‘ENFUSIHIM WE ‘ATEW ‘UTUWÆN KEBIRÆN
  25,22,JEWME JEREWNEL-MELA’IKETE LA BUSHRA JEWME’IDHIN LILMUXHRIMINE WE JEKULUNE HIXHRÆN MEHXHURÆN
  25,23,WE KADIMNA ‘ILA MA ‘AMILU MIN ‘AMELIN FEXHE’ALNAHU HEBA’EN MENTHURÆN
  25,24,‘ESHABUL-XHENNETI JEWME’IDHIN HAJRUN MUSTEKARRÆN WE ‘EHSENU MEKILÆN
  25,25,WE JEWME TESHEKKAKU ES-SEMA’U BIL-GAMAMI WE NUZZILEL-MELA’IKETU TENZILÆN
  25,26,EL-MULKU JEWME’IDHINL-HEKKU LILRREHMENI WE KANE JEWMÆN ‘ALEL-KAFIRINE ‘ASIRÆN
  25,27,WE JEWME JE’ADDU EDH-DHALIMU ‘ALA JEDEJHI JEKULU JA LEJTENI ETTEHADHTU ME’A ER-RESULI SEBILÆN
  25,28,JA WEJLETI LEJTENI LEM ‘ETTEHIDH FULANÆN HALILÆN
  25,29,LEKAD ‘EDELLENI ‘ANI EDH-DHIKRI BA’DE ‘IDH XHA’ENI WE KANE ESH-SHEJTANU LIL’INSANI HADHULÆN
  25,30,WE KALE ER-RESULU JA RABBI ‘INNE KAWMI ETTEHADHU HADHAL-KUR’ANE MEHXHURÆN
  25,31,WE KEDHELIKE XHE’ALNA LIKULLI NEBIJIN ‘ADUWÆN MINEL-MUXHRIMINE WE KEFA BIREBBIKE HADIÆN WE NESIRÆN
  25,32,WE KALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEWLA NUZZILE ‘ALEJHIL-KUR’ANU XHUMLETEN WAHIDETEN KEDHALIKE LINUTHEBBITE BIHI FU’UADEKE WE RETTELNAHU TERTILÆN
  25,33,WE LA JE’TUNEKE BIMETHELIN ‘ILLA XHI’NAKE BIL-HEKKI WE ‘EHSENE TEFSIRÆN
  25,34,EL-LEDHINE JUHSHERUNE ‘ALA WUXHUHIHIM ‘ILA XHEHENNEME ‘ULA’IKE SHERRUN MEKANÆN WE ‘EDELLU SEBILÆN
  25,35,WE LEKAD ‘ATEJNA MUSAL-KITABE WE XHE’ALNA ME’AHU ‘EHAHU HARUNE WEZIRÆN
  25,36,FEKULNA EDH/HEBA ‘ILAL-KAWMIL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA FEDEMMERNAHUM TEDMIRÆN
  25,37,WE KAWME NUHIN LEMMA KEDHDHEBU ER-RUSULE ‘EGREKNAHUM WE XHE’ALNAHUM LILNNASI ‘AJETEN WE ‘A’TEDNA LILDHDHALIMINE ‘ADHABÆN ‘ELIMÆN
  25,38,WE ‘ADÆN WE THEMUDE WE ‘ESHABE ER-RESSI WE KURUNÆN BEJNE DHALIKE KETHIRÆN
  25,39,WE KULLÆN DEREBNA LEHUL-’EMTHALE WE KULLÆN TEBBERNA TETBIRÆN
  25,40,WE LEKAD ‘ETEW ‘ALEL-KARJETI ELLETI ‘UMTIRET METERE ES-SEW’I ‘EFELEM JEKUNU JEREWNEHA BEL KANU LA JERXHUNE NUSHURÆN
  25,41,WE ‘IDHA R’EWKE ‘IN JETTEHIDHUNEKE ‘ILLA HUZUEN ‘EHEDHAL-LEDHI BE’ATHEL-LAHU RESULÆN
  25,42,‘IN KADE LEJUDILLUNA ‘AN ‘ALIHETINA LEWLA ‘EN SEBERNA ‘ALEJHA WE SEWFE JA’LEMUNE HINE JEREWNEL-’ADHABE MEN ‘EDELLU SEBILÆN
  25,43,‘ERE’EJTE MENI ETTEHADHE ‘ILEHEHU HEWAHU ‘EFE’ENTE TEKUNU ‘ALEJHI WE KILÆN
  25,44,‘EM TEHSEBU ‘ENNE ‘EKTHEREHUM JESMA’UNE ‘EW JA’KILUNE ‘IN HUM ‘ILLA KAL’EN’AM BEL HUM ‘EDELLU SEBILÆN
  25,45,‘ELEM TERA ‘ILA RABBIKE KEJFE MEDDE EDH-DHILLE WE LEW SHA’E LEXHE’ALEHU SAKINÆN THUMME XHE’ALNA ESH-SHEMSE ‘ALEJHI DELILÆN
  25,46,THUMME KABEDNAHU ‘ILEJNA KABDÆN JESIRÆN
  25,47,WE HUWEL-LEDHI XHE’ALE LEKUMUL-LEJLE LIBASÆN WE EN-NEWME SUBATÆN WE XHE’ALE EN-NEHARE NUSHURÆN
  25,48,WE HUWEL-LEDHI ‘ERSELE ER-RIJAHE BUSHRÆN BEJNE JEDEJ REHMETIHI WE ‘ENZELNA MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN TEHURÆN
  25,49,LINUHJIJE BIHI BELDETEN MEJTÆN WE NUSKIJEHU MIMMA HALEKNA ‘EN’AMÆN WE ‘ENASIJE KETHIRÆN
  25,50,WE LEKAD SERREFNAHU BEJNEHUM LIJEDHDHEKKERU FE’EBA ‘EKTHERU EN-NASI ‘ILLA KUFURÆN
  25,51,WE LEW SHI’NA LEBE’ATHNA FI KULLI KARJETIN NEDHIRÆN
  25,52,FELA TUTI’IL-KAFIRINE WE XHAHID/HUM BIHI XHIHADÆN KEBIRÆN
  25,53,WE HUWEL-LEDHI MEREXHEL-BEHREJNI HADHA ‘ADHBUN FURATUN WE HEDHA MILHUN ‘UXHAXHUN WE XHE’ALE BEJNEHUMA BERZEHÆN WE HIXHRÆN MEHXHURÆN
  25,54,WE HUWEL-LEDHI HALEKA MINEL-MA’I BESHERÆN FEXHE’ALEHU NESEBÆN WE SIHRÆN WE KANE REBBUKE KADIRÆN
  25,55,WE JA’BUDUNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI MA LA JENFA’UHUM WE LA JEDURRUHUM WE KANEL-KAFIRU ‘ALA RABBIHI DHEHIRÆN
  25,56,WE MA ‘ERSELNAKE ‘ILLA MUBESHSHIRÆN WE NEDHIRÆN
  25,57,KUL MA ‘ES’ELUKUM ‘ALEJHI MIN ‘EXHRIN ‘ILLA MEN SHA’E ‘EN JETTEHIDHE ‘ILA RABBIHI SEBILÆN
  25,58,WE TEWEKKEL ‘ALEL-HEJJIL-LEDHI LA JEMUTU WE SEBBIH BIHEMDIHI WE KEFA BIHI BIDHUNUBI ‘IBADIHI HABIRÆN
  25,59,EL-LEDHI HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE WE MA BEJNEHUMA FI SITTETI ‘EJJAMIN THUMME ESTEWA ‘ALEL-’ARSHI ER-REHMANU FAS’EL BIHI HABIRÆN
  25,60,WE ‘IDHA KILE LEHUM ESXHUDU LILRREHMENI KALU WE MA ER-REHMANU ‘ENESXHUDU LIMA TE’MURUNA WE ZADEHUM NUFURÆN
  25,61,TEBAREKEL-LEDHI XHE’ALE FI ES-SEMA’I BURUXHÆN WE XHE’ALE FIHA SIRAXHÆN WE KAMERÆN MUNIRÆN
  25,62,WE HUWEL-LEDHI XHE’ALEL-LEJLE WE EN-NEHARE HILFETEN LIMEN ‘ERADE ‘EN JEDHDHEKKERE ‘EW ‘ERADE SHUKURÆN
  25,63,WE ‘IBADU ER-REHMANIL-LEDHINE JEMSHUNE ‘ALEL-’ERDI HEWNÆN WE ‘IDHA HATEBEHUMUL-XHAHILUNE KALU SELAMÆN
  25,64,WEL-LEDHINE JEBITUNE LIREBBIHIM SUXHXHEDÆN WE KIJAMÆN
  25,65,WEL-LEDHINE JEKULUNE REBBENA ESRIF ‘ANNA ‘ADHABE XHEHENNEME ‘INNE ‘ADHABEHA KANE GARAMÆN
  25,66,‘INNEHA SA’ET MUSTEKARRÆN WE MUKAMÆN
  25,67,WEL-LEDHINE ‘IDHA ‘ENFEKU LEM JUSRIFU WE LEM JEKTURU WE KANE BEJNE DHALIKE KAWAMÆN
  25,68,WEL-LEDHINE LA JED’UNE ME’A ELLAHI ‘ILEHÆN ‘AHARE WE LA JEKTULUNE EN-NEFSEL-LETI HERREMEL-LAHU ‘ILLA BIL-HEKKI WE LA JEZNUNE WE MEN JEF’AL DHALIKE JELKA ‘ETHAMÆN
  25,69,JUDA’AF LEHUL-’ADHABU JEWMEL-KIJAMETI WE JEHLUD FIHI MUHANÆN
  25,70,‘ILLA MEN TABE WE ‘AMENE WE ‘AMILE ‘AMELÆN SALIHÆN FE’ULA’IKE JUBEDDILU ELLAHU SEJJI’ATIHIM HESENATIN WE KANEL-LAHU GAFURÆN REHIMÆN
  25,71,WE MEN TABE WE ‘AMILE SALIHÆN FE’INNEHU JETUBU ‘ILA ELLAHI METABÆN
  25,72,WEL-LEDHINE LA JESH/HEDUNE EZ-ZURE WE ‘IDHA MERRU BIL-LEGWI MERRU KIRAMÆN
  25,73,WEL-LEDHINE ‘IDHA DHUKKIRU BI’AJATI RABBIHIM LEM JEHIRRU ‘ALEJHA SUMMÆN WE ‘UMJANÆN
  25,74,WEL-LEDHINE JEKULUNE REBBENA HEB LENA MIN ‘EZWAXHINA WE DHURRIJATINA KURRETE ‘A’JUNIN WE EXH’ALNA LILMUTTEKINE ‘IMAMÆN
  25,75,‘ULA’IKE JUXHZEWNEL-GURFETE BIMA SEBERU WE JULEKKAWNE FIHA TEHIJETEN WE SELAMÆN
  25,76,HALIDINE FIHA HESUNET MUSTEKARRÆN WE MUKAMÆN
  25,77,KUL MA JA’BE’U BIKUM RABBI LEWLA DU’A’UUKUM FEKAD KEDHDHEBTUM FESEWFE JEKUNU LIZAMÆN
  26,1,TA-SIN-MIM
  26,2,TILKE ‘AJATUL-KITABIL-MUBINI
  26,3,LE’ALLEKE BAHI’UN NEFSEKE ‘ELLA JEKUNU MU’UMININE
  26,4,‘IN NESHE’ NUNEZZIL ‘ALEJHIM MINE ES-SEMA’I ‘AJETEN FEDHELLET ‘A’NAKUHUM LEHA HADI’INE
  26,5,WE MA JE’TIHIM MIN DHIKRIN MINE ER-REHMANI MUHDETHIN ‘ILLA KANU ‘ANHU MU’RIDINE
  26,6,FEKAD KEDHDHEBU FESEJE’TIHIM ‘ENBA’U MA KANU BIHI JESTEHZI’UN
  26,7,‘EWELEM JEREW ‘ILAL-’ERDI KEM ‘ENBETNA FIHA MIN KULLI ZEWXHIN KERIMIN
  26,8,‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN WE MA KANE ‘EKTHERUHUM MU’UMININE
  26,9,WE ‘INNE REBBEKE LEHUWEL-’AZIZU ER-REHIMU
  26,10,WE ‘IDH NADA REBBUKE MUSA ‘ENI E’TIL-KAWME EDH-DHALIMINE
  26,11,KAWME FIR’AWNE ‘ELA JETTEKUNE
  26,12,KALE RABBI ‘INNI ‘EHAFU ‘EN JUKEDHDHIBUNI
  26,13,WE JEDIKU SEDRI WE LA JENTELIKU LISANI FE’ERSIL ‘ILA HARUNE
  26,14,WE LEHUM ‘ALEJJE DHENBUN FE’EHAFU ‘EN JEKTULUNI
  26,15,KALE KELLA FADH/HEBA BI’AJATINA ‘INNA ME’AKUM MUSTEMI’UNE
  26,16,FE’TIJA FIR’AWNE FEKULA ‘INNA RESULU RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  26,17,‘EN ‘ERSIL ME’ANA BENI ‘ISRA’ILE
  26,18,KALE ‘ELEM NUREBBIKE FINA WELIDÆN WE LEBITHTE FINA MIN ‘UMURIKE SININE
  26,19,WE FE’ALTE FA’LETEKEL-LETI FE’ALTE WE ‘ENTE MINEL-KAFIRINE
  26,20,KALE FE’ALTUHA ‘IDHÆN WE ‘ENA MINE ED-DALLIN
  26,21,FEFERERTU MINKUM LEMMA HIFTUKUM FEWEHEBE LI RABBI HUKMÆN WE XHE’ALENI MINEL-MURSELINE
  26,22,WE TILKE NI’METUN TEMUNNUHA ‘ALEJJE ‘EN ‘ABBEDTE BENI ‘ISRA’ILE
  26,23,KALE FIR’AWNU WE MA REBBUL-’ALEMINE
  26,24,KALE REBBU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA BEJNEHUMA ‘IN KUNTUM MUKININE
  26,25,KALE LIMEN HEWLEHU ‘ELA TESTEMI’UNE
  26,26,KALE REBBUKUM WE REBBU ‘ABA’IKUMUL-’EWWELINE
  26,27,KALE ‘INNE RESULEKUMUL-LEDHI ‘URSILE ‘ILEJKUM LEMEXHNUNUN
  26,28,KALE REBBUL-MESHRIKI WEL-MEGRIBI WE MA BEJNEHUMA ‘IN KUNTUM TA’KILUNE
  26,29,KALE LE’INI ETTEHADHTE ‘ILEHÆN GAJRI LE’EXH’ALENNEKE MINEL-MESXHUNINE
  26,30,KALE ‘EWELEW XHI’TUKE BISHEJ’IN MUBININ
  26,31,KALE FE’TI BIHI ‘IN KUNTE MINE ES-SADIKINE
  26,32,FE’ELKA ‘ASAHU FE’IDHA HIJE THU’BANUN MUBINUN
  26,33,WE NEZE’A JEDEHU FE’IDHA HIJE BEJDA’U LILNNADHIRINE
  26,34,KALE LILMELE’I HEWLEHU ‘INNE HADHA LESAHIRUN ‘ALIMUN
  26,35,JURIDU ‘EN JUHRIXHEKUM MIN ‘ERDIKUM BISIHRIHI FEMADHA TE’MURUNE
  26,36,KALU ‘ERXHIHI WE ‘EHAHU WE EB’ATH FIL-MEDA’INI HASHIRINE
  26,37,JE’TUKE BIKULLI SEHHARIN ‘ALIMIN
  26,38,FEXHUMI’A ES-SEHERETU LIMIKATI JEWMIN MA’LUMIN
  26,39,WE KILE LILNNASI HEL ‘ENTUM MUXHTEMI’UNE
  26,40,LE’ALLENA NETTEBI’U ES-SEHERETE ‘IN KANU HUMUL-GALIBINE
  26,41,FELEMMA XHA’E ES-SEHERETU KALU LIFIR’AWNE ‘E’INNE LENA LE’EXHRÆN ‘IN KUNNA NEHNUL-GALIBINE
  26,42,KALE NE’AM WE ‘INNEKUM ‘IDHÆN LEMINEL-MUKARREBINE
  26,43,KALE LEHUM MUSA ‘ELKU MA ‘ENTUM MULKUNE
  26,44,FE’ELKAW HIBALEHUM WE ‘ISIJEHUM WE KALU BI’IZZETI FIR’AWNE ‘INNA LENEHNUL-GALIBUNE
  26,45,FE’ELKA MUSA ‘ASAHU FE’IDHA HIJE TELKAFU MA JE’FIKUNE
  26,46,FE’ULKIJE ES-SEHERETU SAXHIDINE
  26,47,KALU ‘AMENNA BIREBBIL-’ALEMINE
  26,48,REBBI MUSA WE HARUNE
  26,49,KALE ‘AMENTUM LEHU KABLE ‘EN ‘ADHENE LEKUM ‘INNEHU LEKEBIRUKUMUL-LEDHI ‘ALLEMEKUMU ES-SIHRE FELESEWFE TA’LEMUNE LE’UKATTI’ANNE ‘EJDIJEKUM WE ‘ERXHULEKUM MIN HILAFIN WE LE’USELLIBENNEKUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  26,50,KALU LA DEJRE ‘INNA ‘ILA RABBINA MUNKALIBUNE
  26,51,‘INNA NETMA’U ‘EN JEGFIRE LENA REBBUNA HATAJANA ‘EN KUNNA ‘EWWELEL-MU’UMININE
  26,52,WE ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILA MUSA ‘EN ‘ESRI BI’IBADI ‘INNEKUM MUTTEBA’UNE
  26,53,FE’ERSELE FIR’AWNU FIL-MEDA’INI HASHIRINE
  26,54,‘INNE HA’UULA’ LESHIRDHIMETUN KALILUNE
  26,55,WE ‘INNEHUM LENA LEGA’IDHUNE
  26,56,WE ‘INNA LEXHEMI’UN HADHIRUNE
  26,57,FE’EHREXHNAHUM MIN XHENNATIN WE ‘UJUNIN
  26,58,WE KUNUZIN WE MEKAMIN KERIMIN
  26,59,KEDHALIKE WE ‘EWRETHNAHA BENI ‘ISRA’ILE
  26,60,FE’ETBA’UHUM MUSHRIKINE
  26,61,FELEMMA TERA’AL-XHEM’ANI KALE ‘ESHABU MUSA ‘INNA LEMUDREKUNE
  26,62,KALE KELLA ‘INNE MA’IJE RABBI SEJEHDINI
  26,63,FE’EWHEJNA ‘ILA MUSA ‘ENI EDRIB BI’ASAKEL-BEHRE FANFELEKA FEKANE KULLU FIRKIN KALTTEWDIL-’ADHIMI
  26,64,WE ‘EZLEFNA THEMMEL-’AHARINE
  26,65,WE ‘ENXHEJNA MUSA WE MEN ME’AHU ‘EXHMA’INE
  26,66,THUMME ‘EGREKNAL-’AHARINE
  26,67,‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN WE MA KANE ‘EKTHERUHUM MU’UMININE
  26,68,WE ‘INNE REBBEKE LEHUWEL-’AZIZU ER-REHIMU
  26,69,WE ETLU ‘ALEJHIM NEBE’E ‘IBRAHIME
  26,70,‘IDH KALE LI’EBIHI WE KAWMIHI MA TA’BUDUNE
  26,71,KALU NA’BUDU ‘ESNAMÆN FENEDHELLU LEHA ‘AKIFINE
  26,72,KALE HEL JESMA’UNEKUM ‘IDH TED’UNE
  26,73,‘EW JENFA’UNEKUM ‘EW JEDURRUNE
  26,74,KALU BEL WEXHEDNA ‘ABA’ENA KEDHALIKE JEF’ALUNE
  26,75,KALE ‘EFERE’EJTUM MA KUNTUM TA’BUDUNE
  26,76,‘ENTUM WE ‘ABA’UUKUMUL-’EKDEMUNE
  26,77,FE’INNEHUM ‘ADUWUN LI ‘ILLA REBBEL-’ALEMINE
  26,78,EL-LEDHI HALEKANI FEHUWE JEHDINI
  26,79,WEL-LEDHI HUWE JUT’IMUNI WE JESKINI
  26,80,WE ‘IDHA MERIDTU FEHUWE JESHFINI
  26,81,WEL-LEDHI JUMITUNI THUMME JUHJINI
  26,82,WEL-LEDHI ‘ETMA’U ‘EN JEGFIRE LI HATI’ETI JEWME ED-DINI
  26,83,REBBI HEB LI HUKMÆN WE ‘ELHIKNI BIS-SALIHINE
  26,84,WE EXH’AL LI LISANE SIDKIN FIL-’AHIRINE
  26,85,WE EXH’ALNI MIN WERETHETI XHENNETI EN-NA’IMI
  26,86,WE EGFIR LI’EBI ‘INNEHU KANE MINE ED-DALLINE
  26,87,WE LA TUHZINI JEWME JUB’ATHUNE
  26,88,JEWME LA JENFA’U MALUN WE LA BENUNE
  26,89,‘ILLA MEN ‘ETA ELLAHE BIKALBIN SELIMIN
  26,90,WE ‘UZLIFETIL-XHENNETU LILMUTTEKINE
  26,91,WE BURRIZETIL-XHEHIMU LILGAWINE
  26,92,WE KILE LEHUM ‘EJNE MA KUNTUM TA’BUDUNE
  26,93,MIN DUNI ELLAHI HEL JENSURUNEKUM ‘EW JENTESIRUNE
  26,94,FEKUBKIBU FIHA HUM WEL-GAWUNE
  26,95,WE XHUNUDU ‘IBLISE ‘EXHMA’UNE
  26,96,KALU WE HUM FIHA JEHTESIMUNE
  26,97,TE-ELLAHI ‘IN KUNNA LEFI DELALIN MUBININ
  26,98,‘IDH NUSEWWIKUM BIREBBIL-’ALEMINE
  26,99,WE MA ‘EDELLENA ‘ILLAL-MUXHRIMUNE
  26,100,FEMA LENA MIN SHAFI’INE
  26,101,WE LA SEDIKIN HEMIMIN
  26,102,FELEW ‘ENNE LENA KERRETEN FENEKUNE MINEL-MU’UMININE
  26,103,‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN WE MA KANE ‘EKTHERUHUM MU’UMININE
  26,104,WE ‘INNE REBBEKE LEHUWEL-’AZIZU ER-REHIMU
  26,105,KEDHDHEBET KAWMU NUHINL-MURSELINE
  26,106,‘IDH KALE LEHUM ‘EHUHUM NUHUN ‘ELA TETTEKUNE
  26,107,‘INNI LEKUM RESULUN ‘EMINUN
  26,108,FATTEKU ELLAHE WE ‘ETI’UNI
  26,109,WE MA ‘ES’ELUKUM ‘ALEJHI MIN ‘EXHRIN ‘IN ‘EXHRI ‘ILLA ‘ALA RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  26,110,FATTEKU ELLAHE WE ‘ETI’UNI
  26,111,KALU ‘ENU’UMINU LEKE WE ETTEBE’AKEL-’ERDHELUNE
  26,112,KALE WE MA ‘ILMI BIMA KANU JA’MELUNE
  26,113,‘IN HISABUHUM ‘ILLA ‘ALA RABBI LEW TESH’URUNE
  26,114,WE MA ‘ENA BITARIDIL-MU’UMININE
  26,115,‘IN ‘ENA ‘ILLA NEDHIRUN MUBINUN
  26,116,KALU LE’IN LEM TENTEHI JA NUHU LETEKUNENNE MINEL-MERXHUMINE
  26,117,KALE RABBI ‘INNE KAWMI KEDHDHEBUNI
  26,118,FAFTEH BEJNI WE BEJNEHUM FETHÆN WE NEXHXHINI WE MEN MA’I MINEL-MU’UMININE
  26,119,FE’ENXHEJNAHU WE MEN ME’AHU FIL-FULKIL-MESHHUNI
  26,120,THUMME ‘EGREKNA BA’DUL-BAKINE
  26,121,‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN WE MA KANE ‘EKTHERUHUM MU’UMININE
  26,122,WE ‘INNE REBBEKE LEHUWEL-’AZIZU ER-REHIMU
  26,123,KEDHDHEBET ‘ADUNL-MURSELINE
  26,124,‘IDH KALE LEHUM ‘EHUHUM HUDUN ‘ELA TETTEKUNE
  26,125,‘INNI LEKUM RESULUN ‘EMINUN
  26,126,FATTEKU ELLAHE WE ‘ETI’UNI
  26,127,WE MA ‘ES’ELUKUM ‘ALEJHI MIN ‘EXHRIN ‘IN ‘EXHRI ‘ILLA ‘ALA RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  26,128,‘ETEBNUNE BIKULLI RI’IN ‘AJETEN TA’BETHUNE
  26,129,WE TETTEHIDHUNE MESANI’A LE’ALLEKUM TEHLUDUNE
  26,130,WE ‘IDHA BETESHTUM BETESHTUM XHEBBARINE
  26,131,FATTEKU ELLAHE WE ‘ETI’UNI
  26,132,WE ETTEKUL-LEDHI ‘EMEDDEKUM BIMA TA’LEMUNE
  26,133,‘EMEDDEKUM BI’EN’AMIN WE BENINE
  26,134,WE XHENNATIN WE ‘UJUNIN
  26,135,‘INNI ‘EHAFU ‘ALEJKUM ‘ADHABE JEWMIN ‘ADHIMIN
  26,136,KALU SEWA’UN ‘ALEJNA ‘EWE’ADHTE ‘EM LEM TEKUN MINEL-WA’IDHINE
  26,137,‘IN HADHA ‘ILLA HULUKUL-’EWWELINE
  26,138,WE MA NEHNU BIMU’ADHDHEBINE
  26,139,FEKEDHDHEBUHU FE’EHLEKNAHUM ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN WE MA KANE ‘EKTHERUHUM MU’UMININE
  26,140,WE ‘INNE REBBEKE LEHUWEL-’AZIZU ER-REHIMU
  26,141,KEDHDHEBET THEMUDUL-MURSELINE
  26,142,‘IDH KALE LEHUM ‘EHUHUM SALIHUN ‘ELA TETTEKUNE
  26,143,‘INNI LEKUM RESULUN ‘EMINUN
  26,144,FATTEKU ELLAHE WE ‘ETI’UNI
  26,145,WE MA ‘ES’ELUKUM ‘ALEJHI MIN ‘EXHRIN ‘IN ‘EXHRIJE ‘ILLA ‘ALA RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  26,146,‘ETUTREKUNE FI MA HAHUNA ‘AMININE
  26,147,FI XHENNATIN WE ‘UJUNIN
  26,148,WE ZURU’IN WE NEHLIN TEL’UHA HEDIMUN
  26,149,WE TENHITUNE MINEL-XHIBALI BUJUTÆN FARIHINE
  26,150,FATTEKU ELLAHE WE ‘ETI’UNI
  26,151,WE LA TUTI’U ‘EMREL-MUSRIFINE
  26,152,EL-LEDHINE JUFSIDUNE FIL-’ERDI WE LA JUSLIHUNE
  26,153,KALU ‘INNEMA ‘ENTE MINEL-MUSEHHERINE
  26,154,MA ‘ENTE ‘ILLA BESHERUN MITHLUNA FE’TI BI’AJETIN ‘IN KUNTE MINE ES-SADIKINE
  26,155,KALE HEDHIHI NAKATUN LEHA SHIRBUN WE LEKUM SHIRBU JEWMIN MA’LUMIN
  26,156,WE LA TEMESSUHA BISU’IN FEJE’HUDHEKUM ‘ADHABU JEWMIN ‘ADHIMIN
  26,157,FE’AKARUHA FE’ESBEHU NADIMINE
  26,158,FE’EHADHEHUMUL-’ADHABU ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN WE MA KANE ‘EKTHERUHUM MU’UMININE
  26,159,WE ‘INNE REBBEKE LEHUWEL-’AZIZU ER-REHIMU
  26,160,KEDHDHEBET KAWMU LUTINL-MURSELINE
  26,161,‘IDH KALE LEHUM ‘EHUHUM LUTUN ‘ELA TETTEKUNE
  26,162,‘INNI LEKUM RESULUN ‘EMINUN
  26,163,FATTEKU ELLAHE WE ‘ETI’UNI
  26,164,WE MA ‘ES’ELUKUM ‘ALEJHI MIN ‘EXHRIN ‘IN ‘EXHRIJE ‘ILLA ‘ALA RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  26,165,‘ETE’TUNE EDH-DHUKRANE MINEL-’ALEMINE
  26,166,WE TEDHERUNE MA HALEKA LEKUM REBBUKUM MIN ‘EZWAXHIKUM BEL ‘ENTUM KAWMUN ‘ADUNE
  26,167,KALU LE’IN LEM TENTEHI JA LUTU LETEKUNENNE MINEL-MUHREXHINE
  26,168,KALE ‘INNI LI’AMELIKUM MINEL-KALINE
  26,169,REBBI NEXHXHINI WE ‘EHLI MIMMA JA’MELUNE
  26,170,FENEXHXHEJNAHU WE ‘EHLEHU ‘EXHMA’INE
  26,171,‘ILLA ‘AXHUZÆN FIL-GABIRINE
  26,172,THUMME DEMMERNAL-’AHARINE
  26,173,WE ‘EMTERNA ‘ALEJHIM METERÆN FESA’E METERUL-MUNDHERINE
  26,174,‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN WE MA KANE ‘EKTHERUHUM MU’UMININE
  26,175,WE ‘INNE REBBEKE LEHUWEL-’AZIZU ER-REHIMU
  26,176,KEDHDHEBE ‘ESHABUL-’EJKETIL-MURSELINE
  26,177,‘IDH KALE LEHUM SHU’AJBUN ‘ELA TETTEKUNE
  26,178,‘INNI LEKUM RESULUN ‘EMINUN
  26,179,FATTEKU ELLAHE WE ‘ETI’UNI
  26,180,WE MA ‘ES’ELUKUM ‘ALEJHI MIN ‘EXHRIN ‘IN ‘EXHRIJE ‘ILLA ‘ALA RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  26,181,‘EWFUL-KEJLE WE LA TEKUNU MINEL-MUHSIRINE
  26,182,WE ZINU BIL-KISTASIL-MUSTEKIMI
  26,183,WE LA TEBHASU EN-NASE ‘ESHJA’EHUM WE LA TA’THEW FIL-’ERDI MUFSIDINE
  26,184,WE ETTEKUL-LEDHI HALEKAKUM WEL-XHIBILLETEL-’EWWELINE
  26,185,KALU ‘INNEMA ‘ENTE MINEL-MUSEHHERINE
  26,186,WE MA ‘ENTE ‘ILLA BESHERUN MITHLUNA WE ‘IN NEDHUNNUKE LEMINEL-KADHIBINE
  26,187,FE’ESKIT ‘ALEJNA KISEFÆN MINE ES-SEMA’I ‘IN KUNTE MINE ES-SADIKINE
  26,188,KALE RABBI ‘A’LEMU BIMA TA’MELUNE
  26,189,FEKEDHDHEBUHU FE’EHADHEHUM ‘ADHABU JEWMI EDH-DHULLETI ‘INNEHU KANE ‘ADHABE JEWMIN ‘ADHIMIN
  26,190,‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN WE MA KANE ‘EKTHERUHUM MU’UMININE
  26,191,WE ‘INNE REBBEKE LEHUWEL-’AZIZU ER-REHIMU
  26,192,WE ‘INNEHU LETENZILU RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  26,193,NEZELE BIHI ER-RUHUL-’EMINU
  26,194,‘ALA KALBIKE LITEKUNE MINEL-MUNDHIRINE
  26,195,BILISANIN ‘AREBIJIN MUBININ
  26,196,WE ‘INNEHU LEFI ZUBURIL-’EWWELINE
  26,197,‘EWELEM JEKUN LEHUM ‘AJETEN ‘EN JA’LEMEHU ‘ULEMA’U BENI ‘ISRA’ILE
  26,198,WE LEW NEZZELNAHU ‘ALA BA’DIL-’A’XHEMINE
  26,199,FEKARE’EHU ‘ALEJHIM MA KANU BIHI MU’UMININE
  26,200,KEDHALIKE SELEKNAHU FI KULUBIL-MUXHRIMINE
  26,201,LA JU’UMINUNE BIHI HETTA JEREWL-’ADHABEL-’ELIME
  26,202,FEJE’TIJEHUM BEGTETEN WE HUM LA JESH’URUNE
  26,203,FEJEKULU HEL NEHNU MUNDHERUNE
  26,204,‘EFEBI’ADHABINA JESTA’XHILUNE
  26,205,‘EFERE’EJTE ‘IN METTA’NAHUM SININE
  26,206,THUMME XHA’EHUM MA KANU JU’ADUNE
  26,207,MA ‘EGNA ‘ANHUM MA KANU JUMETTA’UNE
  26,208,WE MA ‘EHLEKNA MIN KARJETIN ‘ILLA LEHA MUNDHIRUNE
  26,209,DHIKRA WE MA KUNNA DHALIMINE
  26,210,WE MA TENEZZELET BIHI ESH-SHEJATINU
  26,211,WE MA JENBEGI LEHUM WE MA JESTETI’UNE
  26,212,‘INNEHUM ‘ANI ES-SEM’I LEMA’ZULUNE
  26,213,FELA TED’U ME’A ELLAHI ‘ILEHÆN ‘AHARE FETEKUNE MINEL-MU’ADHDHEBINE
  26,214,WE ‘ENDHIR ‘ASHIRETEKEL-’EKREBINE
  26,215,WE EHFID XHENAHEKE LIMENI ETTEBE’AKE MINEL-MU’UMININE
  26,216,FE’IN ‘ASEWKE FEKUL ‘INNI BERI’UN MIMMA TA’MELUNE
  26,217,WE TEWEKKEL ‘ALEL-’AZIZI ER-REHIMI
  26,218,EL-LEDHI JERAKE HINE TEKUMU
  26,219,WE TEKALLUBEKE FI ES-SAXHIDINE
  26,220,‘INNEHU HUWE ES-SEMI’UL-’ALIMU
  26,221,HEL ‘UNEBBI’UKUM ‘ALA MEN TENEZZELU ESH-SHEJATINU
  26,222,TENEZZELU ‘ALA KULLI ‘EFFAKIN ‘ETHIMIN
  26,223,JULKUNE ES-SEM’A WE ‘EKTHERUHUM KADHIBUNE
  26,224,WE ESH-SHU’ARA’U JETTEBI’UHUMUL-GAWUNE
  26,225,‘ELEM TERA ‘ENNEHUM FI KULLI WADIN JEHIMUNE
  26,226,WE ‘ENNEHUM JEKULUNE MA LA JEF’ALUNE
  26,227,‘ILLAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI WE DHEKERU ELLAHE KETHIRÆN WE ENTESERU MIN BA’DI MA DHULIMU WE SEJA’LEMUL-LEDHINE DHELEMU ‘EJJE MUNKALEBIN JENKALIBUNE
  27,1,TA-SIN TILKE ‘AJATUL-KUR’ANI WE KITABIN MUBININ
  27,2,HUDEN WE BUSHRA LILMU’UMININE
  27,3,EL-LEDHINE JUKIMUNE ES-SELÆTE WE JU’UTUNE EZ-ZEKÆTE WE HUM BIL-’AHIRETI HUM JUKINUNE
  27,4,‘INNEL-LEDHINE LA JU’UMINUNE BIL-’AHIRETI ZEJJENNA LEHUM ‘A’MALEHUM FEHUM JA’MEHUNE
  27,5,‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE LEHUM SU’UL-’ADHABI WE HUM FIL-’AHIRETI HUMUL-’EHSERUNE
  27,6,WE ‘INNEKE LETULEKKAL-KUR’ANE MIN LEDUN HEKIMIN ‘ALIMIN
  27,7,‘IDH KALE MUSA LI’HLIHI ‘INNI ‘ANESTU NARÆN SE’ATIKUM MINHA BIHABERIN ‘EW ‘ATIKUM BISHIHABIN KABESIN LE’ALLEKUM TESTELUNE
  27,8,FELEMMA XHA’EHA NUDIJE ‘EN BURIKE MEN FI EN-NARI WE MEN HEWLEHA WE SUBHANEL-LAHI RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  27,9,JA MUSA ‘INNEHU ‘ENALLAHUL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  27,10,WE ‘ELKI ‘ASAKE FELEMMA RE’AHA TEHTEZZU KE’ENNEHA XHANNUN WELLA MUDBIRÆN WE LEM JU’AKKIB JA MUSA LA TEHAF ‘INNI LA JEHAFU LEDEJJEL-MURSELUNE
  27,11,‘ILLA MEN DHELEME THUMME BEDDELE HUSNÆN BA’DE SU’IN FE’INNI GAFURUN REHIMUN
  27,12,WE ‘EDHIL JEDEKE FI XHEJBIKE TEHRUXH BEJDA’E MIN GAJRI SU’IN FI TIS’I ‘AJATIN ‘ILA FIR’AWNE WE KAWMIHI ‘INNEHUM KANU KAWMÆN FASIKINE
  27,13,FELEMMA XHA’ET/HUM ‘AJATUNA MUBSIRETEN KALU HADHA SIHRUN MUBINUN
  27,14,WE XHEHEDU BIHA WE ESTEJKANET/HA ‘ENFUSUHUM DHULMÆN WE ‘ULUWÆN FANDHUR KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-MUFSIDINE
  27,15,WE LEKAD ‘ATEJNA DAWUDE WE SULEJMANE ‘ILMÆN WE KALAL-HEMDU LILLAHIL-LEDHI FEDDELENA ‘ALA KETHIRIN MIN ‘IBADIHIL-MU’UMININE
  27,16,WE WERITHE SULEJMANU DAWUDE WE KALE JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ‘ULLIMNA MENTIKAT-TEJRI WE ‘UTINA MIN KULLI SHEJ’IN ‘INNE HADHA LEHUWEL-FEDLUL-MUBINU
  27,17,WE HUSHIRE LISULEJMANE XHUNUDUHU MINEL-XHINNI WEL-’INSI WET-TEJRI FEHUM JUZA’UNE
  27,18,HETTA ‘IDHA ‘ETEW ‘ALA WADI EN-NEMLI KALET NEMLETUN JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NEMLU EDHULU MESAKINEKUM LA JEHTIMENNEKUM SULEJMANU WE XHUNUDUHU WE HUM LA JESH’URUNE
  27,19,FETEBESSEME DAHIKÆN MIN KAWLIHA WE KALE RABBI ‘EWZI’NI ‘EN ‘ESHKURE NI’METEKEL-LETI ‘EN’AMTE ‘ALEJJE WE ‘ALA WE E-DEJJE WE ‘EN ‘A’MELE SALIHÆN TERDAHU WE ‘EDHILNI BIREHMETIKE FI ‘IBADIKE ES-SALIHINE
  27,20,WE TEFEKKADET-TEJRE FEKALE MA LI LA ‘ERAL-HUD/HUDE ‘EM KANE MINEL-GA’IBINE
  27,21,LE’U’ADHDHIBENNEHU ‘ADHABÆN SHEDIDÆN ‘EW LE’EDHBEHENNEHU ‘EW LEJE’TIJENI BISULTANIN MUBININ
  27,22,FEMEKETHE GAJRE BA’IDIN FEKALE ‘EHETTU BIMA LEM TUHIT BIHI WE XHI’TUKE MIN SEBE’IIN BINEBE’IIN JEKININ
  27,23,‘INNI WE XHEDTTU EMRE’ETEN TEMLIKUHUM WE ‘UTIJET MIN KULLI SHEJ’IN WE LEHA ‘ARSHUN ‘ADHIMUN
  27,24,WE XHEDTUHA WE KAWMEHA JESXHUDUNE LILSHSHEMSI MIN DUNI ELLAHI WE ZEJJENE LEHUMU ESH-SHEJTANU ‘A’MALEHUM FESEDDEHUM ‘ANI ES-SEBILI FEHUM LA JEHTEDUNE
  27,25,‘ELLA JESXHUDU LILLAHIL-LEDHI JUHRIXHUL-HAB’E FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE JA’LEMU MA TUHFUNE WE MA TU’LINUNE
  27,26,ELLAHU LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE REBBUL-’ARSHIL-’ADHIMI
  27,27,KALE SENENDHURU ‘ESEDEKTE ‘EM KUNTE MINEL-KADHIBINE
  27,28,EDH/HEB BIKITABI HADHA FE’ELKIH ‘ILEJHIM THUMME TEWELLE ‘ANHUM FANDHUR MADHA JERXHI’UNE
  27,29,KALET JA ‘EJJUHAL-MELE’U ‘INNI ‘ULKIJE ‘ILEJJE KITABUN KERIMUN
  27,30,‘INNEHU MIN SULEJMANE WE ‘INNEHU BISMI ELLAHI ER-REHMANI ER-REHIMI
  27,31,‘ELLA TA’LU ‘ALEJJE WE ‘TUNI MUSLIMINE
  27,32,KALET JA ‘EJJUHAL-MELE’U ‘EFTUNI FI ‘EMRI MA KUNTU KATI’ATEN ‘EMRÆN HETTA TESH/HEDUNI
  27,33,KALU NEHNU ‘ULU KUWETIN WE ‘ULU BE’SIN SHEDIDIN WEL-’EMRU ‘ILEJKI FANDHURI MADHA TE’MURINE
  27,34,KALET ‘INNEL-MULUKE ‘IDHA DEHALU KARJETEN ‘EFSEDUHA WE XHE’ALU ‘A’IZZETE ‘EHLIHA ‘EDHILLETEN WE KEDHELIKE JEF’ALUNE
  27,35,WE ‘INNI MURSILETUN ‘ILEJHIM BIHEDIJETIN FENADHIRETUN BIME JERXHI’UL-MURSELUNE
  27,36,FELEMMA XHA’E SULEJMANE KALE ‘ETUMIDDUNENI BIMALIN FEMA ‘ATANIJEL-LAHU HAJRUN MIMMA ‘ATAKUM BEL ‘ENTUM BIHEDIJETIKUM TEFREHUNE
  27,37,ERXHI’ ‘ILEJHIM FELENE’TIJENNEHUM BIXHUNUDIN LA KIBELE LEHUM BIHA WE LENUHRIXHENNEHUM MINHA ‘EDHILLETEN WE HUM SAGIRUNE
  27,38,KALE JA ‘EJJUHAL-MELE’U ‘EJJUKUM JE’TINI BI’ARSHIHA KABLE ‘EN JE’TUNI MUSLIMINE
  27,39,KALE ‘IFRJTUN MINEL-XHINNI ‘ENA ‘ATIKE BIHI KABLE ‘EN TEKUME MIN MEKAMIKE WE ‘INNI ‘ALEJHI LEKAWIJUN ‘EMINUN
  27,40,KALEL-LEDHI ‘INDEHU ‘ILMUN MINEL-KITABI ‘ENA ‘ATIKE BIHI KABLE ‘EN JERTEDDE ‘ILEJKE TERFUKE FELEMMA RE’AHU MUSTEKIRRÆN ‘INDEHU KALE HADHA MIN FEDLI RABBI LIJEBLUWENI ‘E’ESHKURU ‘EM ‘EKFURU WE MEN SHEKERE FE’INNEMA JESHKURU LINEFSIHI WE MEN KEFERE FE’INNE
  27,41,KALE NEKKIRU LEHA ‘ARSHEHA NENDHUR ‘ETEHTEDI ‘EM TEKUNU MINEL-LEDHINE LA JEHTEDUNE
  27,42,FELEMMA XHA’ET KILE ‘EHEKEDHA ‘ARSHUKI KALET KE’ENNEHU HUWE WE ‘UTINAL-’ILME MIN KABLIHA WE KUNNA MUSLIMINE
  27,43,WE SEDDEHA MA KANET TA’BUDU MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘INNEHA KANET MIN KAWMIN KAFIRINE
  27,44,KILE LEHA EDHULI ES-SERHE FELEMMA RE’ET/HU HESIBET/HU LUXHXHETEN WE KESHEFET ‘AN SAKAJHA KALE ‘INNEHU SERHUN MUMERREDUN MIN KAWARIRE KALET RABBI ‘INNI DHELEMTU NEFSI WE ‘ESLEMTU ME’A SULEJMANE LILLAHI RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  27,45,WE LEKAD ‘ERSELNA ‘ILA THEMUDE ‘EHAHUM SALIHÆN ‘ENI A’BUDU ELLAHE FE’IDHA HUM FERIKANI JEHTESIMUNE
  27,46,KALE JA KAWMI LIME TESTA’XHILUNE BIS-SEJJI’ETI KABLEL-HESENETI LEWLA TESTEGFIRUNEL-LAHE LE’ALLEKUM TURHEMUNE
  27,47,KALU ETTEJJERNA BIKE WE BIMEN ME’AKE KALE TA’IRUKUM ‘INDEL-LAHI BEL ‘ENTUM KAWMUN TUFTENUNE
  27,48,WE KANE FIL-MEDINETI TIS’ATU REHTIN JUFSIDUNE FIL-’ERDI WE LA JUSLIHUNE
  27,49,KALU TEKASEMU BILLAHI LENUBEJJITENNEHU WE ‘EHLEHU THUMME LENEKULENNE LIWELIJIHI MA SHEHIDNA MEHLIKE ‘EHLIHI WE ‘INNA LESADIKUNE
  27,50,WE MEKERU MEKRÆN WE MEKERNA MEKRÆN WE HUM LA JESH’URUNE
  27,51,FANDHUR KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETU MEKRIHIM ‘ENNA DEMMERNAHUM WE KAWMEHUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  27,52,FETILKE BUJUTUHUM HAWIJETEN BIMA DHELEMU ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN LIKAWMIN JA’LEMUNE
  27,53,WE ‘ENXHEJNAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE KANU JETTEKUNE
  27,54,WE LUTÆN ‘IDH KALE LIKAWMIHI ‘ETE’TUNEL-FAHISHETE WE ‘ENTUM TUBSIRUNE
  27,55,‘E’INNEKUM LETE’TUNE ER-RIXHALE SHEHWETEN MIN DUNI EN-NISA’ BEL ‘ENTUM KAWMUN TEXHHELUNE